**Full Study Roadmap Page Specification** created at `docs/design/pages/full-study-roadmap-spec.md` (726 lines, 47KB).

The document covers:

- **Page purpose & user goals** — long-term journey view from today to exam day
- **14 current UX/UI problems** identified from the actual `RoadmapPage.tsx` implementation (flat accordion, no timeline, weak today highlight, no phase celebrations, no AI Tutor integration, cramped mobile)
- **Proposed layout** with visual ASCII diagram showing header, phase timeline, phase sections (completed/current/upcoming), day cards, summary, and AI insight
